<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-10767] Checking version of Cassandra command creates `cassandra.logdir_IS_UNDEFINED/`</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-10767</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When I execute `cassandra -v` on the terminal the directory `cassandra.logdir_IS_UNDEFINED` is created in my CWD:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;$ tree cassandra.logdir_IS_UNDEFINED
cassandra.logdir_IS_UNDEFINED
&#9492;&#9472;&#9472; system.log

0 directories, 1 file
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Expected: That no log file nor directory is created when I&apos;m simply checking the version of Cassandra. Feels a bit ridiculous.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Additionals: Just double checking, is this a bundling issue that should be reported to Homebrew? Probably not, right?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;$ cassandra -v                                                                                                                    &lt;br/&gt;
2.1.2&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;MacOSX 10.9.5&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;$ brew info cassandra                                                                                                              &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;14:15:41&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
cassandra: stable 2.2.3 (bottled)&lt;br/&gt;
Eventually consistent, distributed key-value store&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://cassandra.apache.org&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://cassandra.apache.org&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
/usr/local/Cellar/cassandra/2.1.2 (3975 files, 92M) *&lt;br/&gt;
  Built from source&lt;br/&gt;
From: &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/Homebrew/homebrew/blob/master/Library/Formula/cassandra.rb&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/Homebrew/homebrew/blob/master/Library/Formula/cassandra.rb&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
==&amp;gt; Caveats&lt;br/&gt;
To have launchd start cassandra at login:&lt;br/&gt;
  ln -sfv /usr/local/opt/cassandra/*.plist ~/Library/LaunchAgents&lt;br/&gt;
Then to load cassandra now:&lt;br/&gt;
  launchctl load ~/Library/LaunchAgents/homebrew.mxcl.cassandra.plist&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
