                            <comment id="15116527" author="yukim" created="Tue, 26 Jan 2016 02:30:25 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt&gt;cassandra -v&lt;/tt&gt; invokes main method in &lt;tt&gt;GetVersion&lt;/tt&gt; class, which trigger logback initialization through access to FBUtilities. We need to add &quot;-Dcassandra.logdir=...&quot; when using &apos;-v&apos; switch as well.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I will go through other scripts including windows one to make sure we are passing above. Scripts for tools should be using logback-tools.xml instead so I will check that as well.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15138008" author="yukim" created="Mon, 8 Feb 2016 23:36:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I ended up only fixing cassandra scripts for both *nix/windows.&lt;br/&gt;
